			</div>
			<div class="respons-full">
				<table class="table table-bordered">
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<th>尺寸</th>
						<td>54mm(W)×130mm(L) ×27mm(H)</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>重量</th>
						<td>108g</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>电源</th>
						<td>DC:6V~30V</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>使用温度</th>
						<td>-25℃ ~ +65℃</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>环境适应性</th>
						<td>耐肥料、防锈剂附着、耐氯化钙侵蚀、抗振动、抗冲击、防水、耐盐水、抗油污、耐汽油、防尘、抗紫外线、防凝露、</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>蜂窝通信</th>
						<td>・4G LTE Cat 1频段 (1,2,3,4,5,7,8,12,19,20,26,28,38)<br />
						・3G UMTS Band 8</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>GNSS</th>
						<td>GPS、GLONASS、Galileo、北斗、准天顶系统</td>
					</tr>
